-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| File                   | Purpose                                                        |
| ---------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `/etc/passwd`          | Stores basic user info (username, UID, shell, home directory). |
| `/etc/group`           | Stores group info.                                             |
| `/etc/shadow`          | Stores encrypted passwords.                                    |
| `/etc/fstab`           | Defines disk partitions and mount points.                      |
| `/etc/hostname`        | Contains system hostname.                                      |
| `/etc/hosts`           | Maps hostnames to IPs (local DNS).                             |
| `/etc/sudoers`         | Defines sudo (admin) privileges.                               |
| `/etc/ssh/sshd_config` | SSH server configuration.                                      |


